OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLGBT veterans: Government  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FU-turn on Commons debate   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The treatment of veterans thrown out of
OL,6, the military for being gay will be the 
OL,7, subject of a full debate in Parliament,
OL,8, after a government U-turn.             
OL,10,FLGBT people were banned from serving in
OL,11,Fthe armed forces until the year 2000.  
OL,13,FThe debate, originally promised in     
OL,14,FJuly, after an independent report into 
OL,15,Fthe ban, was then scrapped but, BBC    
OL,16,FNews has learned, will now be in 2024. 
OL,18,FAnd veterans affected can now register 
OL,19,Ftheir interest in applying for         
OL,20,Freparative schemes.                    
